Description copied from interface: OnsgmlsOutputParser
Invokes ANTLR parser on ESIS file passed as input parameter. Returns parser object which, after parse, maintains accumulated feature information about the SGML file, which will be accessed by the SgmlModule class to report properties about the file

Specified by:

Parameters:
